methods.void append(int key, boolean value): Puts a key/value pair into the array, optimizing for the case where the key is greater than all existing keys in the array.
methods.void clear(): Removes all key-value mappings from this SparseBooleanArray.
methods.SparseBooleanArray clone(): Creates and returns a copy of this object.
methods.void delete(int key): Removes the mapping from the specified key, if there was any.
methods.boolean equals(Object that): Indicates whether some other object is "equal to" this one.
methods.boolean get(int key): Gets the boolean mapped from the specified key, or false if no such mapping has been made.
methods.boolean get(int key, boolean valueIfKeyN: Gets the boolean mapped from the specified key, or the specified value if no such mapping has been made.
methods.int hashCode(): Returns a hash code value for the object.
methods.int indexOfKey(int key): Returns the index for which keyAt(int) would return the specified key, or a negative number if the specified key is not mapped.
methods.int indexOfValue(boolean value): Returns an index for which valueAt(int) would return the specified key, or a negative number if no keys map to the specified value.
methods.int keyAt(int index): Given an index in the range 0...size()-1, returns the key from the indexth key-value mapping that this SparseBooleanArray stores.
methods.void put(int key, boolean value): Adds a mapping from the specified key to the specified value, replacing the previous mapping from the specified key if there was one.
methods.void removeAt(int index): Removes the mapping at the specified index.
methods.void setValueAt(int index, boolean value: Directly set the value at a particular index.
methods.int size(): Returns the number of key-value mappings that this SparseBooleanArray currently stores.
methods.String toString(): Returns a string representation of the object. This implementation composes a string by iterating over its mappings.
methods.boolean valueAt(int index): Given an index in the range 0...size()-1, returns the value from the indexth key-value mapping that this SparseBooleanArray stores.
